---
title: Double Slow-Cooked Peppercorn Beef Stew with Potato Mash & Parsley
description: Snuggle up with this warm, homey beef stew, packed with veggies and herbs to add an aromatic touch. Cradled on a bed of
fluffy creamy mashed potato and stirred through with a peppercorn sauce, it’s guaranteed to bring a cosy end to the day
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64a20a6a63263fe66c41e666-66057b8a.jpeg
